162
00:08:45,019 --> 00:08:46,159
Tunggu.

163
00:08:50,789 --> 00:08:53,600
Lihat dirimu. Beginikah caramu cuti?

164
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:57,470
Sudah kubilang. Aku introver.

165
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,899
Beginilah cara pria introver menghabiskan cutinya.

166
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,779
Mari kita lihat.

167
00:09:15,649 --> 00:09:18,690
Rekaman ini sudah lama, jadi, kualitas suara mungkin tidak bagus.

168
00:09:23,659 --> 00:09:25,830
