169
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:29,470
Aku melaporkan kecelakaan mobil. Tolong cepat.

170
00:09:29,570 --> 00:09:31,470
Tolong tenang, Bu.

171
00:09:31,539 --> 00:09:33,269
Di mana lokasimu?

172
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:36,570
Lokasiku? Itu...

173
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:38,509
Ini Rute Tujuh.

174
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:40,080
Cepatlah.

175
00:09:40,139 --> 00:09:42,810
Kamu bilang itu kecelakaan mobil. Bisa jelaskan secara detail?

176
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:45,950
Sebuah mobil terbalik. Tolong cepat datang!

177
00:09:46,019 --> 00:09:48,389
Apa yang terjadi?

178
00:09:49,149 --> 00:09:50,419
Halo?

179
00:09:51,289 --> 00:09:54,930
Kami tahu dia menghubungi kami lewat telepon di dekat sini.

180
00:10:02,869 --> 00:10:04,300
Aku ingin mengambil ini.

181
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:12,379
Apa kamu mengingat semua yang kukatakan kepadamu?

182
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,539
- Ya!
- Ya!

183
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:17,450
Kalau begitu, katakan dengan keras. Mulai.

184
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:20,919
Satu. Kalian harus saling membantu selama masa sulit.

185
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:24,989
Dua. Kesediaan adalah yang terpenting.

186
00:10:25,090 --> 00:10:26,259
Sa Rang.

187
00:10:26,419 --> 00:10:27,989
Berapa kali harus kuulangi?

188
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,629
