189
00:10:29,690 --> 00:10:30,960
Kesetiaan.

190
00:10:31,029 --> 00:10:32,629
Benar. Kesediaan.

191
00:10:33,529 --> 00:10:35,100
Ini serius.

192
00:10:35,930 --> 00:10:37,129
Sa Rang.

193
00:10:37,230 --> 00:10:40,669
Bagaimana kamu akan mengencani pria dari Seoul jika dia tidak paham?

194
00:10:40,999 --> 00:10:42,169
Ikuti aku.

195
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,710
"Cuacanya dingin."

196
00:10:44,779 --> 00:10:46,539
"Cuacanya berangin."

197
00:10:46,610 --> 00:10:48,310
Dingin, bukan berangin.

198
00:10:48,379 --> 00:10:49,950
Benar. Dingin.

199
00:10:50,009 --> 00:10:52,350
Itu dia. Coba sekali lagi.

200
00:10:52,419 --> 00:10:54,989
"Cuacanya dingin.."

201
00:10:55,090 --> 00:10:57,050
"Cuacanya berangin."

202
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:02,789
Baiklah. Berbicara tidak penting saat berkencan.

203
00:11:03,259 --> 00:11:05,430
Bahasa tubuh saja sudah cukup.

204
00:11:06,129 --> 00:11:07,700
Kita kehabisan waktu.

205
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:12,639
Astaga. Hanya butuh 50 menit.

206
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,239
Bantu aku selama 50 menit saja.

207
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,710
Kamu pasti bisa.

208
00:11:15,769 --> 00:11:16,840
Semoga berhasil.

209
00:11:16,909 --> 00:11:19,940
Kamu pengganti ibu bagiku.

210
00:11:20,009 --> 00:11:22,350
"Kontes Menyanyi Nasional"

211
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:26,350
Ibu!

212
00:11:31,019 --> 00:11:33,820
"Kontes Menyanyi Nasional"

