Semua orang tampak sangat siap.

215
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:40,300
Aku sama sekali tidak bersiap.

216
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:48,210
Astaga.

217
00:11:49,669 --> 00:11:50,810
Apa kau NORAZO?

218
00:11:51,509 --> 00:11:53,639
Tidak, ada NORAZO.

219
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:56,480
Tapi kami ANNORAZO.

220
00:11:57,249 --> 00:11:59,950
Itu sangat menarik. Kalian sangat mirip.

221
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,350
