229
00:12:24,139 --> 00:12:26,539
Bisakah kamu mendengarkan laguku sekarang?

230
00:12:27,110 --> 00:12:28,180
Mari kita dengar.

231
00:12:28,249 --> 00:12:31,749
Satu. Satu. Satu, dua, tiga, empat.

232
00:12:31,850 --> 00:12:36,249
"Angin berembus"

233
00:12:36,889 --> 00:12:41,730
"Ke dalam hatiku yang sedih"

234
00:12:41,789 --> 00:12:42,930
Tidak!

235
00:12:42,989 --> 00:12:46,300
